{
  "name": "OLEObjects",
  "summary": "<p>每一个 <strong>OLEObject</strong> 对象都代表一个 ActiveX 控件或一个链接或嵌入的 OLE 对象。<br>在 JS 环境中添加到工作表上的控件不是ActiveX 控件，所以 <strong>OLEObjects</strong> 集合中不包括这些JS控件。</p>\n<p>工作表上的 ActiveX 控件有两个名称：一个是包含该控件的形状（Shape）对象的名称（查看工作表时，可在选择窗格中看到此名称）；另一个是控件的代码名称（在“属性”窗口的“(名称)”右侧单元格中可看到此名称）。第一次向工作表添加控件时，形状名称和代码名称是一致的。但是，如果您更改这两个名称中的任意一个，另一个不会随之自动更改。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/OLEObjects/OLEObjects .htm#OLEObjects.OLEObjects\">OLEObjects</a></strong> 方法可返回 <strong>OLEObjects</strong> 集合。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*下例在第一个工作表上隐藏所有 OLE 对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">OLEObjects</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Visible</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>使用 <a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/OLEObjects/OLEObjects .htm#OLEObjects.Add\"><strong>Add</strong></a> 方法可创建一个新 OLE 对象并将它添加到 <strong>OLEObjects</strong> 集合中。</p>\n<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*下例在第一个工作表中创建表示图片文件 Arcade.gif 的新 OLE 对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">OLEObjects</span>().<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;arcade.gif&quot;</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*下例在第一张工作表中新建一个 ActiveX 控件（一个列表框）。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">OLEObjects</span>().<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Forms.ListBox.1&quot;</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>在控件事件函数名中使用的是控件的代码名称，但是，当您从工作表的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Shapes/Shapes .htm#Shapes.Shapes\">Shapes</a></strong> 或 <strong>OLEObjects</strong> 集合中返回控件时，必须使用形状名称而不是代码名称，以便按名称引用控件。另外，在 JS 环境中添加的控件（非ActiveX 控件）只允许修改形状名称，不允许修改代码名称。例如，假定您给工作表添加一个复选框，而默认的形状名称和代码名称都是 CheckBox1。如果您修改了该复选框的形状名称，但在控件事件函数名中仍须使用 CheckBox1，如下例所示</p>\n<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例假定存在名为CheckBox1的JS控件，单击此控件触发如下事件，则显示JS控件对应的shape_chk1（改过的形状名称）左上角单元格地址*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">CheckBox1_Click</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;shape_chk1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TopLeftCell</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Address</span>())\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>指定工作表中所有 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/OLEObject/OLEObject .htm#OLEObject.OLEObject\">OLEObject</a></strong> 对象的集合。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Application/Application .htm#Application.Application\">Application</a></strong> 对象，该对象表示 ET 应用程序。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个表示指定对象（可对一个 OLE 自动操作对象使用本属性来返回该对象的应用程序）创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>){\n  <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject 的应用程序的消息。*/</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>){\n      <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n  }\n  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span>{\n      <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n  }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Border",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Border/Border .htm#Border.Border\">Border</a></strong> 对象，它代表对象的边框。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例将工作表 Sheet1 中所有 OLE 对象的边框粗细设置为细线。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> border = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">OLEObjects</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Border</span>\n    border.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Weight</span> = xlHairline\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示活动工作表中所有 OLE 对象边框的 TintAndShade 属性值是否为0。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> border = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">OLEObjects</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Border</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(border.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span> == <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Border",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Count",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Long</strong> 值，它代表集合中对象的数量。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示工作表 Sheet1 中 OLE 对象的数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">OLEObjects</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Enabled",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果启用对象，则为 <strong>True</strong>。<strong>Boolean</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例启用活动工作表中的所有 OLE 对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">OLEObjects</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Enabled</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例禁用第一张工作表中的所有 OLE 对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">OLEObjects</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Enabled</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Height",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong>Double</strong> 值，它代表对象的高度（以磅为单位）。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示活动工作表中所有 OLE 对象的高度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">OLEObjects</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Height</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例将第一张工作表中所有 OLE 对象高度设置为45磅。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">OLEObjects</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Height</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">45</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（double 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Left",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置 <strong>Double</strong> 值，它代表从对象左边缘到工作表的 A 列左边缘或图表上的图表区左边缘的距离（以磅为单位）。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示活动工作表中所有 OLE 对象左边缘到工作表的 A 列左边缘的距离。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">OLEObjects</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Left</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例将第一张工作表中所有 OLE 对象左边缘到工作表的 A 列左边缘的距离设置为10磅。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">OLEObjects</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Left</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（double 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Locked",
      "summary": "<p>如果对象已被锁定，此属性将返回 <strong>True</strong>；如果在工作表处于受保护状态时仍能修改对象，则返回 <strong>False</strong>。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong>Boolean</strong> 值，它指明对象是否已被锁定。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示活动工作表中所有 OLE 对象是否已被锁定。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">OLEObjects</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Locked</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例取消第一张工作表中所有 OLE 对象的锁定。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">OLEObjects</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Locked</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Placement",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个包含 **<a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlPlacement 枚举.html\">XlPlacement</a>**常量的 <strong>Variant</strong> 值，它代表对象附加到它所在的单元格的方式。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示活动工作表中所有 OLE 对象附加到它所在的单元格的方式是否为对象随单元格移动和调整大小。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">OLEObjects</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Placement</span> == xlMoveAndSize)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例将第一张工作表中所有 OLE 对象附加到它所在的单元格的方式设置为自由浮动。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">OLEObjects</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Placement</span> = xlFreeFloating\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "PrintObject",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果打印文档时也打印指定对象，则为 <strong>True</strong>。<strong>Boolean</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例设置第一张工作表中所有 OLE 对象在打印文档时也打印该对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">OLEObjects</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">PrintObject</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示在打印文档时活动工作表中所有 OLE 对象是否打印。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">OLEObjects</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">PrintObject</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "ShapeRange",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/ShapeRange/ShapeRange .htm#ShapeRange.ShapeRange\">ShapeRange</a></strong> 对象，它代表指定的一个或多个对象。只读。</p>\n",
