    },
    {
      "name": "ZOrder",
      "summary": "<p>在任何对象集合中，z-次序尾端的对象为 <em>collection</em>(1)，z-次序前端的对象为 <em>collection</em>(<em>collection</em>.<strong>Count</strong>)。例如，如果活动工作表中有嵌入图表，z-次序尾端的图表为 <code>ActiveSheet.ChartObjects(1)</code>，z-次序前端的图表为 <code>ActiveSheet.ChartObjects(ActiveSheet.ChartObjects.Count)</code>。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的 z-次序位置。<strong>Long</strong> 型，只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例在工作表 Sheet1 中新建一个文档 OLE 对象，并显示其z-次序位置*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>)\n    sheet.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">OLEObjects</span>().<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Word.Document.12&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`OLE 对象集合的z-次序位置为<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${sheet.OLEObjects().ZOrder}</span>`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例在第一张工作表中由文件创建一个 OLE 对象，并显示其z-次序位置*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    sheet.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">OLEObjects</span>().<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D:/data.xlsx&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;data.xlsx&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`OLE 对象集合的z-次序位置为<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${sheet.OLEObjects().ZOrder}</span>`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    }
